        "path": "/v2/{+name}"
      },
      "python_call": "svc.projects().locations().keys().delete(**params).execute()",
      "description": "Deletes an API key. Deleted key can be retrieved within 30 days of deletion. Afterward, key will be purged from the project. NOTE: Key is a global resource; hence the only supported value for location",
